# Demo Skill Implementation

## Commands

### hello
Says hello to the user.

```prose
command hello {
  output "Hello! This is the demo skill speaking."
}
```

### echo
Echoes back the user's input.

```prose
command echo {
  input "What would you like me to echo?"
  output "You said: {{input}}"
}
```

## Example Usage

```
@demo-skill hello
@demo-skill echo This is a test
```
